snippet.title: Diana and Roma Go on Ski Vacation in the French Alps - Family Fun Trip
snippet.description:
Finally, Diana and Roma have a winter vacation! The whole family went on a ski vacation in the French Alps! Here the nature is of incredible beauty and very steep snow slides! Diana and Roma ski all day! Super active family travel!
Thanks for watching!
